---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Zach Louden">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-20 md:pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-6">
      About
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-tight mb-10">
      I'm Zach, a product designer based in the San Francisco Bay Area.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-ink)]/90">
      <p>
        I believe software design can make people's lives better and more
        enjoyable — especially the kind of software people stare at all day.
        Most of my career has been spent on complex systems modeling and
        data‑heavy applications used in professional contexts.
      </p>
      <p>
        I've led design on tools that help states submit Medicaid data from
        over 74 million patients, redesigned 30‑year‑old aircraft planning
        systems at FedEx, and built design systems from scratch at StreamSets
        and HashiCorp. Lately I've been working independently — designing
        complex SaaS UX <em>and</em> building the software.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside work, I like cooking and fermenting things, reading on the
        train, and spending time at Ocean Beach with my dog. I'm also
        slowly learning Russian.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] italic">
        «Совершенство достигается не тогда, когда уже нечего прибавить, а
        когда уже ничего нельзя отнять.»
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-line)] flex flex-wrap gap-8 text-sm">
      <a href="/resume" class="hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">View resume →</a>
      <a href="mailto:zlouden@gmail.com" class="hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">Email me →</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zacharylouden/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">LinkedIn →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
